  "title": "Crunchy Syrian Nut Stir-fry",
  "description": "A lazy-sunday dish featuring a rich and crunchy blend of scotch bonnet and bhuna spices in a nut-free-friendly version.",
  "cuisine": "Syrian",
  "diet": null,
